      'a video showed a man abusing migrant workers and assaulting them on a moving train in tamil nadu. the video posted by right wing supporter karthik gopinath is now going viral on social media platforms.\nin the 2-minute long video, a man, speaking in tamil, can be seen abusing and assaulting other men belonging to other states (migrant workers) inside a jam-packed train.\nadvertisement\nlater in the video, the man even grabs, pulls the other men by the hair, and blows a couple of punches despite calls to stop.\nmeanwhile, when india today spoke to officials from the southern railway, they said that they are unaware of this incident and are looking into it.\nhowever, an fir in the case was registered under sections 153 a, 323 and 294 (b) of the ipc after the video went viral.\nfurther investigations are on.',
